===subject:labels
===from:Heidi Edsill
===date:Tue Feb 15 13:42:41 2000
===message:I agree with you about labels.  The public definately has a right to know whether the products they are consuming are genetically modified.  While it appears that most GM products are safe for human use, the public should be given the choice of using them or not.  Also, if companies agree to this, it shows confidence in their GM products.  Otherwise, it appears that they have something to hide.
